Whether you’re a frequent flier or a busy student you’ll love how easy it is to clean and how much you can store inside. There’s ample storage for your books, laptops, and tech accessories inside. If you’re heading out to busy halls, libraries or parks to study, give it a delicate cycle in the wash with cold water and air dry afterward.
